<p>The Courier is a critial part of the bloodline of your colony. They will run from workerâ€™s hut to <a href="../../source/buildings/warehouse">Warehouse</a> to workerâ€™s hut, visiting all your workers and delivering the tools and materials they need as well as taking their production to the Warehouse.</p>

<p>The level of the Courierâ€™s Hut will dictate how much materials/tools the Courier can carry to/from Huts - Warehouse - Huts, so if you want them to carry more materials/tools, upgrade the Courierâ€™s Hut. Also, the higher the level of the hut, the faster the Courier will run.</p>

