<h3 id="note-you-must-build-the-warehouse-to-at-least-level-1-so-the-courier-can-do-their-work">Note: You MUST build the Warehouse to at least level 1 so the Courier can do their work.</h3>

<h3 id="note-you-can-have-up-to-10-couriers-per-warehouse-the-default-configuration-only-allows-for-1-warehouse-but-this-can-be-changed-however-couriers-assigned-to-subsequent-warehouses-will-only-see-the-items-in-the-warehouse-they-are-assigned-to">Note: You can have up to 10 Couriers per Warehouse. The default configuration only allows for 1 Warehouse, but this can be changed. However, Couriers assigned to subsequent Warehouses will only see the items in the Warehouse they are assigned to.</h3>
